cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.SOC, cs.IR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper analyzes the reach of junk news on Facebook, which is a social network platform.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also likely as the paper discusses the societal impact of junk news on Facebook users.
- cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences) is another possible category as the paper examines user interactions with junk news and mainstream news on Facebook, which involves social and behavioral aspects.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper involves analyzing and comparing the reach of different types of news on Facebook.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper may involve analyzing the multimedia content of junk news and mainstream news on Facebook.
